## Consultation Points

Claude **must stop and get user approval** before:
1. Transitioning from Stage 1 (planning) to Stage 2 (implementation)
2. Transitioning from Stage 2 (implementation) to Stage 3 (commit)
3. Propagating findings from retro to the bootstrap template
4. Any destructive git operation

